STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Marko WHITLOCK, Appellant. No. ED 106650 Missouri Court of Appeals, Eastern District, DIVISION ONE. Filed: June 11, 2019 Mary S. Choi, 1010 Market Street, Suite 1100, St. Louis, MO. 63101, for appellant. Nathan J. Aquino, P.O. Box 899, Jefferson City, MO. 65102, for respondent. Before Roy L. Richter, P.J., Robert M. Clayton, III, J., and Angela T. Quigless, J.

ORDER

PER CURIAM

Marko Whitlock appeals the judgment of the trial court entered upon a jury verdict convicting him of third-degree domestic assault, Section 565.074 RSMo., second-degree domestic assault, Section 565.073 RSMo., and fourth-degree domestic assault, Section 565.076 RSMo. No jurisprudential purpose would be served by a written opinion. We have furnished the parties with a memorandum, for their information only, setting forth the reasons for our order. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
